  <brief_title>Posaconazole vs Itraconazole in Preventing IFD Post-HSCT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Posaconazole Oral Suspension and Itraconazole Oral Solution in Preventing Invasive Fungal Disease (IFD) in Patients With Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
