  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Invasive Fungal Disease (IFD) after haematopoietic stem cell transplantation (HSCT) remain a
      clinical challenge.The studay aims to compare the efficacy and safety of posaconazole oral
      suspension vs itraconazole oral solution in preventing IFD post-HSCT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
